\c 111
\s Vanhu ngavarumbidze Jehovha nokuda kwezvose zvaakaita
\p
\v 1 Hareruya! Ndichavonga Jehovha nomwoyo wangu wose, Parangano yavakarurama, napaungano.
\
\v 2 Mabasa aJehovha makuru, Anocherechedzwa navose vanoafarira.
\p
\v 3 Basa rake rinoratidza kukudzwa noumambo;
\s Kururama kwake kunogara nokusingaperi.
\p
\v 4 Mabasa ake, anoshamisa, wakaaita chiyeudziro;
\s Jehovha anenyasha netsitsi.
\p
\v 5 Akapa zvokudya vanomutya; Acharangarira sungano yake nokusingaperi.
\p
\v 6 Akaratidza vanhu vake simba ramabasa ake,
\s Zvaakavapa nhaka yavahedheni.
\p
\v 7 Mabasa amaoko ake izvokwadi nokururamisira;
\s Mirairo yake yose yakasimba.
\p
\v 8 Yakasimbiswa nokusingaperi-peri, Yakaitwa nezvokwadi nokururama.
\p
\v 9 Akatumira vanhu vake rudzikinuro; Akaraira sungano yake nokusingaperi;
\s Zita rake idzvene rinotyisa.
\p
\v 1 Â° Kutya Jehovha ndiko kutanga kwouchenjeri;
\s Vose vanozviita vanomurangariro wakanaka;
\s Kurumbidzwa kwake kunogara nokusingaperi.
